        "text": "regulations complying with the law."
      },
      {
        "start": 25.04,
        "end": 28.0,
        "text": "By which I mean certain judges are not following the laws and"
      },
      {
        "start": 28.0,
        "end": 30.44,
        "text": "are trying to do what they want instead."
      },
      {
        "start": 30.44,
        "end": 33.6,
        "text": "The federal judges want to make decisions on their own terms."
      },
      {
        "start": 33.6,
        "end": 38.72,
        "text": "They are issuing very high bond awards as well as denials of bond in asylum cases,"
      },
      {
        "start": 38.72,
        "end": 40.2,
        "text": "for example."
      },
      {
        "start": 40.2,
